          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJ-MWA5K6tmUZsXW-X7vEVvuDDWUJO0vGXCHdUiT2Pe71uVww=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Save yourself the headache; go to a different pharmacy/location.\n\nThis location consistently drops the ball. For example, I\u2019ve requested refills and been told the medicine is out of stock and will be ordered and filled within 2 days. When this happens, they never fill the prescription as promised (and yes this has happened several times). It always requires me calling them after 5-7 days, at which point they can fill the prescription immediately because the medicine was successfully restocked but they never followed through and filled the prescription automatically like they said they would. One time I asked a pharmacist a simple question about what OTC medicine to use for an illness and the pharmacist clearly rushed, didn\u2019t process what I said and blurted out the wrong answer. A customer overheard and told me the correct answer which a simple google search confirmed. And, no, the pharmacy was not busy with customers and this was outside of peak hours. Another time they returned my filled prescriptions earlier than they should have. When I went to pick them up, I had to wait for them to refill the prescriptions again.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tVNFZGcGpkMXBRTmpoclVFa3RiRkl0UkRjeWJuYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x2cc1b72ca3975eda!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOkU4VFpjd1pQNjhrUEktbFItRDcybnc%7C%7C?hl=en",
