          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWh3qA59hezZDDOOb3wYgvAXMC9leIHZsStPI8XNXq1LMsRkxFC=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "Everything is now locked behind a lock while they Have 1 or less workers on staff, so u will wait 20mins for someone to help you OR u can just walk to Walgreens faster instead!  Its extremely ridiculous to lock up $5 items NOONE is stealing too. Like way to ensure NOONE buys theee by forcing ppl to be embarrassed buying denture cream or pads. Sooo biased against eldelry",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21sWGQweE9jMU40VG5SWGNrVnRZMWgyYjNWVFNVRRAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x2cc1b72ca3975eda!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOmlXd0xOc1N4TnRXckVtY1h2b3VTSUE%7C%7C?hl=en",
          "date": "7 months ago",
